mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "From the Floor", "Square Dance Datebook", "As I See It", "Gold Ribbon Report: Dancer Associations", "Association Directory", "Past Officers", "Gold Ribbon Report: The Big Event", "The Dancer's Walkthru", "Madeline Allen: The People Who Square Dance", "Style Lab: A Gimmick Grand Square", "National Convention", "Round the World of Square Dancing", "S.I.O. Workshop", "Caller of the Month: Art Shepherd-Christchurch, N.Z.", "A Big Day for a Great Guy", "On The Record", "Current Best Sellers", and "Feature Fashion".
